trans-unit.source: Establishes an inline editor for the updating of property values.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter et innebygd redigeringsprogram for oppdatering av egenskapsverdier.

trans-unit.source: This class can hold a single <xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate>: one for an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainerEditMode> editor.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan inneholde én <xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate>: én for en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainerEditMode>redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainerEditMode> </xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate>

trans-unit.source: Inline editing refers to the entering of property values into a text box or similar control as opposed to setting the value by choosing it from a drop-down menu.
trans-unit.target: Innebygd redigering refererer til å angi verdier i en tekstboks eller lignende kontroll i stedet for angivelse av verdien ved å velge den fra en rullegardinmenyen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> class as the specified <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainer.InlineEditorTemplate*>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"> </xref> klassen som den angitte <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainer.InlineEditorTemplate*>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainer.InlineEditorTemplate*>

trans-unit.source: The inline editor <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> used to create the new property value editor.
trans-unit.target: Redigeringsprogrammet for innebygd <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"> </xref> brukes til å opprette den nye egenskapen redigeringsprogram for verdi.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref> to designate that a particular <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> be used to change a property value.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"> </xref> til å angi at en bestemt <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"> </xref> brukes til å endre en egenskapsverdi.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> for which to create the new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref>.

Creates a new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref> to designate that a particular <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> type be used to change a property value.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"> </xref> til å angi at en bestemt <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"> </xref> brukes til å endre en egenskapsverdi.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> type for which to create the new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"> </xref> type å opprette den nye <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref> for the designated <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"></xref> type.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"> </xref> for den angitte <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor"> </xref> type.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the InlineEditorTemplate, the <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> that is used for an inline editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir InlineEditorTemplate den <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"> </xref> som brukes for en innebygd redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: This <xref:System.Windows.DataTemplate> has its <xref:System.Windows.DataContext> set to a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue>.
A <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> that represents an inline editor.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"> </xref> som representerer en innebygd redigeringsprogrammet.
